# Motor Control â€“ Manual & Automatic Modes (PLC + HMI)

This project implements a motor control system using CODESYS PLC.

Features:
- Manual and Automatic operating modes
- Start / Stop / Emergency Stop logic
- State machine (IDLE, STARTING, RUNNING, FAULT)
- HMI with pushbuttons and status lamps
- TON-based startup delay
- Safety interlocks

Technology:
- CODESYS (Ladder + Visualization)
- IEC 61131-3

Screenshots included.
